("Right" Crotale relpied as he began walking.  He used his radars 
to 
link directly back to the Autobot ship.  Everything he could see 
was now in front of JetV back at the ship.

"Slag kill him" he roared as he transformed into his tricerotop mode 
and charged.  

"No.." Crotale said quietly as he shot at energy net over the beast, 
not stopping him though.  "Why did you bring him Pacifix, this may 
not help in the greater cause."

Back in the Hidden One JetV got the incoming transmissions.    
"Oh Matrix look at the destruction" he called out to whoever was 
there.  "Can you believe it??")
